title: The Breakfast Club Talks Sesame Place, Donkey of The Day, Desus & Mero and More
itunes:title: The Breakfast Club Talks Sesame Place, Donkey of The Day, Desus & Mero and More
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we ask our callers if they have ever been racially profiled against at theme parks in wake of everything that happened at a Sesame Place theme park. During Rumor Report Yee talks about the ending of Desus & Mero on Showtime. Charlamagne gives us our Tuesday Donkey of The Day
